==English==
===Variants===
[[folderal]], [[falderal]] or [[fal-de-ral]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#Nonsense word traditional to English [[ballad]]s and [[madrigal]]s.
#Something of little value; a trinket.
#Excess effort expended on a trivial subject; much ado about nothing.

*''Fol-de-rol and fiddle dee dee and fiddley faddley foddle all the wishes in the world are poppy cock and twoddle.'' -- lyrics to Richard Rogers' Cinderella.

